commit.message: Fixed slime target problem, occurred because slimes were dying, and fixed player attacks not doing damage, mana was being subtracted twice.

Fixed doDamage error, was caused by slime attack target never being set. New errors: player does no damage with a strike (attack that needs no mana) when he has no mana, and slimes all do the minimum amount of damage.
Tried to simplify doDamage loop, ended up with all attacks doing damage at seperate times... What the?
Got companion doDamage working, player mana attack doesnt seem to be working though. Heals are working, just the mana attack is bugged.
Got doDamage method working with Slime iteration in main loop.
Added damage + attack sprite declarations to Entity constructor, added doDamage method to Entity class.
Small changies
Updated Entity documentation.
Fixed sprite positioning for slimes.
Fully integrated Sprite class, TODO: fix slime sprites not updating their position correctly.
Added support for Sprite in Slime class, fixed paint method in Entity class to not draw 2 sprites when damaged.
Started working on integrating Sprite into other classes, got it integrated with Entity, Player and Slime still need checking and thingamajigs.
Changed entity array in main to an ArrayList.
Changed setName and then updateImage to just updateImage(String), began work on Sprite class. TODO: implement Sprite class into Entity class.
Added isMob boolean in Entity, to prevent non - mobs painting healthbars and damage frames. I am terrible.

Created and added Character class as child of enity and parent to all things with health and things. Going to change it to a boolean unfucking the entity paint method and making it only paint healthbars if this shits a character. All that work wasted. Fuck.
Changed attack loop to using entities array only, and to be one loop for all entities.
Updated enemy attack code.
Lots of things.
Fixed enemies not dying. TODO: balance mana usage / attack power.
Fixed player using mana at inopportune times... I think?
Got player and companion universal targets working.
Added array of entities, converted paint to using it.
Fixed companion not being targeted by slimes.
Fixed slimes not taking damage. TODO: Fix slimes not targeting companion.
Converted attacks totaking damage to use negative and positive attack power.
Deleted heal things, movesets need to be reworked completely.ompletely.
Added player's healing moves.

All old features restored. WOOOOT.
